{"tid":2209985,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"施覺民劈炮 英議員：正直者難忍國安法","createTime":"2020-09-20T05:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T06:54:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fe423a946ec004ac8113a5df735e9483817ff955","tid":2209985,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:25:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/YF2JXVIKYBGUDM4OYY56WZSYGY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2FYF2JXVIKYBGUDM4OYY56WZSYGY%2F&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE1uZLtDw6XEhdFI90r4xbX0%3D&h=1aef72fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2FYF2JXVIKYBGUDM4OYY56WZSYGY%2F&h=715c0b67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/YF2JXVIKYBGUDM4OYY56WZSYGY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n施覺民劈炮 英議員：正直者難忍國安法<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】終審法院非常任法官施覺民（James Spigelman）在特首林鄭月娥宣佈香港沒有三權分立翌日「劈炮」，提早兩年離任。施覺民接受傳媒訪問時表明，辭任與港版國安法有關。英國保守黨前黨魁、下議員施志安（Iain Duncan Smith）接受外媒訪問時直言，事件反映在北京及國安法下，正直的人已被置於無法忍受的制度中，並指這是司法獨立地方不會發生的問題。政務司長張建宗堅稱，國安法絕對沒有令一國兩制倒退，而是令香港長治久安。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Onx_OVSIiby1M0pX4HKpNZglKiY=/1181x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OIEH4EIZQND6VMVKR24W725LNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOnx_OVSIiby1M0pX4HKpNZglKiY%3D%2F1181x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOIEH4EIZQND6VMVKR24W725LNY.jpg&h=38a2aeb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■英保守黨前黨魁施志安憂慮法官將要為極權掩飾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/A-0C4_1OiUqsFQaMxtsYN2_NsR8=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NNIJDNTSGFBQ7KJITWUAAIIWWQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FA-0C4_1OiUqsFQaMxtsYN2_NsR8%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNNIJDNTSGFBQ7KJITWUAAIIWWQ.jpg&h=cf4ed077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■施覺民早前辭任終院法官，直指與國安法有關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n促英審視法官在港工作安排<br />\n<br />\n一直關注中國和香港情況的施志安接受《悉尼先驅晨報》訪問時說，擔心獨立的法官在未來需要為極權進行掩飾，建議英國審視英國法官在香港終審法院的工作安排，並形容香港目前情況是把正直的人置於無法忍受的制度中（exposing decent people to intolerable structures），這是英國或澳洲等司法獨立的地方不會出現的問題，必須立即處理。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗昨接受電台訪問時稱，希望外界尊重施覺民個人意願，。。。。。。。。。。。。，不影響營商，反而推動香港長治久安。<br />\n<br />\n對於三權分立的爭議，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，香港行政、立法、司法機關乃各司其職。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人昨回應傳媒查詢，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，港版國安法絕對不會影響香港的司法獨立和司法制度的運作，包括終院。<br />\n<br />\n發言人又指，海外非常任法官參與終審法院審判，。。。。。。。<br />\n。。。，會繼續維持香港委任其他普通法地區法官的制度。"},{"pid":"fdba1724fdfcda86586211a6ab81cd04786ecd44","tid":2209985,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:32:23.000Z","msg":"香港警察好崇拜架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3819c0639294948bd1a00ef7780f9c6e9934826","tid":2209985,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22c4387bec258e49f8110f87a957395e43eb88a","tid":2209985,"uid":650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}